### What Is Spring Cloud Services?

Spring Cloud Services for VMware Tanzu packages the server-side components of [Spring Cloud Config](https://spring.io/projects/spring-cloud-config) and [Spring Cloud Netflix](https://spring.io/projects/spring-cloud-netflix) Eureka, making them available as services in the VMware Tanzu Application Service for VMs Marketplace.

